Request Parameter To Required

Api Url :- https://developerbazaar.com/api/
Method To Send :- POST
Request Parameter Required :- 
            1.request = "Which Kind Of Request i.e Wordpress Website, Ecommerce Website".
	    2.amount = "Amount which paid to us i.e 100,200".
            3.currency = "Currency which you have to paid to us i.e EURO,USD"



Response To Get 
1.When Sender method is wrong.
{
  "status": "error",
  "message": "Request Method Choose Wrong",
  "error_code": 0
}

2.When Parameter field are missing.
{
  "status": "error",
  "message": "Some Parameter is missing or wrong",
  "error_code": 0
}
3.When Transaction Created Succesfully !.
{
  "status": "success",
  "message": "Transaction Created Successfully !",
  "error_code": 1,
  "transaction_id": "607457ef7bc99"
}



Data Sync Hooks to get data

Api Url :- https://developerbazaar.com/api/transaction

Response To Get

{
  "transaction_id": "607457ef7bc99",
  "timestamp": "",
  "request": "testing",
  "amount": "10",
  "currency": "euro",
  "ip": "49.36.39.15",
  "status": "success"
}
